'''The statue of ''St. Proclus''''' (1494–1495) was created by [[Michelangelo]] out of [[marble]].  Its height is 58.5&nbsp;cm.  It is situated in the [[Basilica of San Domenico]], [[Bologna]].  Its subject is [[Saint Proculus of Bologna|Saint Proculus (Proculus)]], a [[martyr]] of Bologna.

